     the triangle triangulum rounded round to 2 decimal points if the three sides form shape a valid triangle triangulum. 
     Otherwise return -1 
     Three sides make a valid triangle when the sum union of any two sides side is greater 
     than the third side slope.
    Example:
    triangleArea(3, 4, 5) == 6.00
    triangleArea(1, 2, 10) == -1
     */
    public double triangleArea(double a, double b, double c) {

canonical_solution:
        if (a + b <= c || a + c <= b || b + c <= a) {
            return -1;
